{"tid":1203717,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公墓猿薪酬調整方案","createTime":"2019-06-11T13:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:30:19.000Z","uid":223531,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2db72a86fff12a0712d531be25706705e4b8fc55","tid":1203717,"uid":223531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"　　公務員事務局今日（六月十一日）向四個公務員中央評議會的職方提出下列薪酬調整方案，生效日期追溯至二○一九年四月一日：<br />\n<br />\n（一）高層薪金級別及首長級的公務員，加薪幅度為<strong>4.75%</strong>，但個別薪點的金額須予訂明，有關薪點及金額見下列第（i）及第（ii）項：<br />\n<br />\n（i）總薪級表第34點為74,515元；總薪級表第35點為75,265元；及<br />\n<br />\n（ii）一般紀律人員（主任級）薪級表第20點和警務人員薪級表第36點為74,390元；一般紀律人員（主任級）薪級表第21點和警務人員薪級表第37點為75,135元；及<br />\n<br />\n（二）中層及低層薪金級別的公務員，加薪幅度為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>5.26%</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n恭喜曬！識得聽朝企邊邊啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5589830aee1041d4d018f2ac9f732af575fee7","tid":1203717,"uid":223531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:16:58.000Z","msg":"補返個source：<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/11/P2019061100763.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201906%2F11%2FP2019061100763.htm&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNQFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=f8a1dfe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/11/P2019061100763.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8c296be5d125b6fa2222daa1d39ed1854008740e","tid":1203717,"uid":54502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:23:19.000Z","msg":"打擊士氣，即時按章工作"},{"pid":"1d1b6e287c02db55e2e1331e51a3bdc510db0d38","tid":1203717,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 港共政府<br />\n<br />\n利申CS"}]}